I"	<h2 id="指定-scoop-安装目录">指定 Scoop 安装目录</h2>

<p>环境变量：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>SCOOP='D:\Applications\Scoop'
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="指定安装程序自定义目录">指定安装程序自定义目录</h2>

<p>设置 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">SCOOP</code> 环境变量后，程序会默认安装在 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">%SCOOP%\apps</code> 目录下。</p>

<p>还可以自定义全局安装目录：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>SCOOP_GLOBAL='D:\Applications\ScoopApps'
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>这样需要 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">scoop install -g &lt;appname&gt;</code> 来全局安装，需要使用管理员权限执行。</p>

<h2 id="加快下载速度">加快下载速度</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>scoop install aria2
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="软件下载">软件下载</h2>

<p>安装到默认目录：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>scoop install &lt;appname&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>安装到全局安装目录：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>scoop install -g &lt;appname&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>软件搜索：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>scoop search &lt;appname&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>列出已知 bucket：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>scoop bucket known
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>添加 bucket：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>scoop bucket add &lt;bucketname&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="查看软件信息">查看软件信息</h2>

<p>列出已安装软件：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>scoop list
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>查看某软件信息：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>scoop info &lt;appname&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>
